				<div class="comment-body"><p>JJ, there is more about the Hugo Awards than just who the current year&#8217;s finalists are. The front page of the web site is the most recent news about the Hugo Awards, with links to information available at the top of the page. Obviously to you the current year&#8217;s finalists are the most important information, but other people come to the web site for other information about the Awards.</p>
