				<div class="comment-body"><p>Thanks for pointing that out. I&#8217;ve updated that page to point to the WSFS rules page and included a note warning people that TheHugoAwards.org, WSFS.org, and individual Worldcons&#8217; web sites are maintained separately from each other and are not necessarily updated on a coordinated schedule because Worldcons are so decentralized and because WSFS doesn&#8217;t have a &#8220;central office&#8221; that runs everything.</p>
</div>

