				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a3d9503fd392c0fa3df136520cf578d6?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a3d9503fd392c0fa3df136520cf578d6?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn">Y. C.</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
