				<div class="comment-body"><p>I&#8217;ve read that the song &#8220;In the Year 2525&#8221; was nominated for a Hugo Award.  Has a Hugo Award ever been given to any music?  In looking briefly over the categories and searching at this site, I get no returns for &#8220;music&#8221; at all and see no evidence of music having been awarded a Hugo Award.  Thank you in advance for your reply.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=455649#respond' data-commentid="455649" data-postid="11" data-belowelement="comment-455649" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Y. C.'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
