				<div class="comment-body"><p>You don&#8217;t &#8220;submit work&#8221; for the Hugo Awards. See <a href="../../index.html?page_id=191" rel="nofollow">Submitting Your Work</a> for more details.</p>
<p>There is no age limit for either Hugo Award nominees or for people to make nominations. Any person of any age can be nominated for a Hugo Award. Any person of any age can nominate works or people for Hugo Awards.</p>
</div>

