				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0705662246d5cad23562a62592fb21da?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0705662246d5cad23562a62592fb21da?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.rocketstackrank.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Eric Wong</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
