				<div class="comment-body"><p>Question about Best Graphic Story:</p>
<p>For a volume published in 2015 which collects issues which were all previously published in 2014, is the volume then ineligible for the 2016 Hugo?</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=472491#respond' data-commentid="472491" data-postid="11" data-belowelement="comment-472491" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Laura'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
