				<div class="comment-body"><p>Alenadro:</p>
<p>You do not send your novel to anyone. This is not a contest that you enter. You cannot &#8220;submit&#8221; a work for consideration for the Hugo Awards. Nominations for the Hugo Awards are submitted by the thousands of members of the World Science Fiction Society, and those five works in each category with the most nominations go on to a final ballot. There is no submission process.</p>
<p>See our article regarding <a href="../../index.html?page_id=191" rel="nofollow">Submissions</a> for more information.</p>
</div>

