				<div class="comment-body"><p>Yes. Eligibility for the Hugo Award has nothing to do with any award other than the Hugo Award. For example, some works have won both the Nebula and Hugo Awards.</p>
<p>Kevin Standlee<br />
Hugo Awards/WSFS Web Site Team</p>
