				<div class="comment-body"><p>Graphic works are not explicitly <em>excluded</em> from the new Award for Best Young Adult Book. The 2018 Hugo Award Administrator (who is also responsible for administering the 2018 YA Book Award and John W. Campbell Award) has not expressed a public opinion on the subject. Therefore, we cannot say for certain whether such works would be ruled eligible if they received sufficient nominations to make the final ballot.</p>
</div>

