				<div class="comment-body"><p>The ballots themselves are administered by individual Worldcon committees, not by TheHugoAwards.org or even by a centralized organization, so you would have to contact the individual Worldcon committees to ask that question. However, recent administrators have stated that they will not release such data, even &#8220;anonymized,&#8221; because they believe it would be too easy to determine how specific individuals voted.</p>
</div>

