				<div class="comment-body"><p>Olav:</p>
<p>The reason we had no list for 1956 was that the historical data we had from which our original listings were drawn did not include it. Thank you for bringing this historical document to our attention. We have updated the listing accordingly.</p>
<p>The voting for 1956 was clearly conducted much differently from modern Hugo Award balloting. In particular, there was room for write-in votes on the final ballot, and it appears that voting was &#8220;first past the post.&#8221; Also, in one category, there were no finalists at all; for Best Professional Magazine, all votes were write-ins.</p>
</div>

