				<div class="comment-body"><p>Assaf:</p>
<p>Serialized works are eligible for the year of the appearance/publication of the final installment. Therefore, the series that ended in 2017 is eligible for the 2018 Hugo Awards. The series that began in 2017 but has not yet finished is not eligible for the 2018 Hugo Awards.</p>
</div>

