				<div class="comment-body"><p>Can  short story be considered part of a series?  And if an arc of 23 novels, four novelettes, and a short story is broken down into four sub-series, can all of them be considered for the Best Series Hugo?</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=539280#respond' data-commentid="539280" data-postid="11" data-belowelement="comment-539280" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Jonathan Brazee'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
